2026-03-30T07:03:55.8253436Z             "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Add tests for email preview exception handling in customer Detail page (covers catch block in LoadEmailPreviewAsync)\r\n- Add tests for malformed JSON parsing in activity summary (motion and temperature readings with invalid JSON)\r\n- Add concurrent export lock contention test for sanitized database export (About page)\r\n- Add SendTimeHelper boundary tests: exact-at-now times, DST spring-forward UTC conversion, null/whitespace fallback paths\r\n- Add DatabaseBackupService tests: cancellation handling, InitializeStats error resilience, file timestamp verification\r\n- Add TokenRefreshService tests: retry exhaustion with token unchanged, graceful cancellation during delay\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- `tests/Hpoll.Admin.Tests/Customers/DetailModelTests.cs` — 5 new tests: email preview exception handling, malformed motion/temperature JSON, missing \"changed\" property\r\n- `tests/Hpoll.Admin.Tests/AboutModelTests.cs` — 1 new test: concurrent export returns lock contention error\r\n- `tests/Hpoll.Core.Tests/SendTimeHelperTests.cs` — 7 new tests: boundary conditions, DST spring-forward UTC validation, fallback chains\r\n- `tests/Hpoll.Worker.Tests/DatabaseBackupServiceTests.cs` — 4 new tests: cancellation logging, InitializeStats error path, file timestamp stats\r\n- `tests/Hpoll.Worker.Tests/TokenRefreshServiceTests.cs` — 3 new tests: retry exhaustion, cancellation during delay\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\n\r\n- [x] All 585 tests pass locally (247 Admin, 155 Worker, 183 Core)\r\n- [ ] CI build passes on branch\r\n- [ ] Coverage reports confirm improved line/branch rates for Detail.cshtml.cs, About.cshtml.cs, SendTimeHelper.cs, DatabaseBackupService.cs, TokenRefreshService.cs\r\n",
